prompt: Create a generative painting titled "Mystical Abyss" that captures the essence of the original artwork, "Still Life from the Sea with Tentacles." Combine elements of traditional still life arrangements with fantastical tentacles emerging from the depths of the sea. Use vibrant colors and intricate details to bring the seashells, corals, and pearls to life. The tentacles should intertwine delicately with the still life objects, conveying a sense of enchantment and mystery. Set the composition against a dark backdrop to enhance the surreal atmosphere. Let your imagination run wild and explore the boundaries of reality and fantasy
